Text: RE EISL Agency Agreement Amendment Proposal Cc I have attached the proposed amendment to the Agency Agreement for your review Sara subject to comments I would appreciate it if you could also coordinate signatures Note that I will be out of the office until August Please contact Janine if you have any questionscomments Kind regards Steve Original Message From Glover Sheila Sent July To Juggins Janine Shackleton Sara Cc Jacobson Stephen Subject EISL Agency Agreement Amendment Proposal Janine and Sara The attached memo supports the proprosal to amend the Agency Agreement to July st for compensation purposes Please advise Sheila
